com.kontakt.sdk.android.data

Enum ServiceModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ServiceModel>
      • com.kontakt.sdk.android.data.ServiceModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ServiceModel>

    public enum ServiceModel
extends Enum<ServiceModel>
    Service Model describes service propagated by kontakt.io beacon after connecting to it. For more information refer to kontakt.io Beacon specification - version 2.0.
    See Also:
    kontakt.io Beacon Datasheet - version 2.0.
